,{"t":"t","i":["lh80ZHuglIgi",1],"o":"start","l":43,"c":"Myth 10: “Immigrant integration has failed”","b":[{"t":"a","x":"YQ2DwxxHVZs79hJzz6kEtQ","l":"","i":["lh80ZHuglIgi",44],"s":{"i":["lh80ZHuglIgi",1],"a":"b"},"e":{"i":"end","a":"b"},"a":["b"]}]},{"t":"e","b":[]}],"l":""},"c":[]}}}},"crdt_format_version":1,"created_time":1758809362629,"last_edited_time":1758809362689,"parent_id":"277a8836-e820-80e3-88ef-cbe1c00c3dd0","parent_table":"block","alive":true,"created_by_table":"notion_user","created_by_id":"222d872b-594c-8128-886d-0002585be925","last_edited_by_table":"notion_user","last_edited_by_id":"222d872b-594c-8128-886d-0002585be925"},"role":"editor"}},"279a8836-e820-80f3-a37f-e0e4397744a0":{"spaceId":"8c4a8836-e820-8133-9c30-00030263b38c","value":{"value":{"id":"279a8836-e820-80f3-a37f-e0e4397744a0","space_id":"8c4a8836-e820-8133-9c30-00030263b38c","version":3,"type":"text","properties":{"title":[["The narrative of “failed integration” is misleading. While challenges exist, de Haas shows that immigrants and their descendants generally integrate over time, especially across generations. Indicators like language acquisition, educational attainment, and labor participation steadily improve. However, structural inequalities — such as racism, discrimination, and class barriers — slow the process. The “failure” narrative exaggerates cultural differences and ignores the long historical reality that integration has always been gradual and uneven."]]},"crdt_data":{"title":{"r":"knFHEDUF6LW81CNR1mU-cw,\"start\",\"end\"","n":{"knFHEDUF6LW81CNR1mU-cw,\"start\",\"end\"":{"s":{"x":"knFHEDUF6LW81CNR1mU-cw","i":[{"t":"s"},{"t":"t","i":["bmSOCpgnbBW0",1],"o":"start","l":550,"c":"The narrative of “failed integration” is misleading. While challenges exist, de Haas shows that immigrants and their descendants generally integrate over time, especially across generations. Indicators like language acquisition, educational attainment, and labor participation steadily improve. However, structural inequalities — such as racism, discrimination, and class barriers — slow the process. The “failure” narrative exaggerates cultural differences and ignores the long historical reality that integration has always been gradual and uneven."},{"t":"e"}],"l":""},"c":[]}}}},"crdt_format_version":1,"created_time":1758809362631,"last_edited_time":1758809362689,"parent_id":"277a8836-e820-80e3-88ef-cbe1c00c3dd0","parent_table":"block","alive":true,"created_by_table":"notion_user","created_by_id":"222d872b-594c-8128-886d-0002585be925","last_edited_by_table":"notion_user","last_edited_by_id":"222d872b-594c-8128-886d-0002585be925"},"role":"editor"}},"279a8836-e820-80b3-8ad9-ed934be365e0":{"spaceId":"8c4a8836-e820-8133-9c30-00030263b38c","value":{"value":{"id":"279a8836-e820-80b3-8ad9-ed934be365e0","space_id":"8c4a8836-e820-8133-9c30-00030263b38c","version":4,"type":"sub_sub_header","properties":{"title":[["Myth 11: “Mass migration has produced mass segregation”",[["b"]]]]},"crdt_data":{"title":{"r":"U35ZbzLo8UbynZbCBqHm9A,\"start\",\"end\"","n":{"U35ZbzLo8UbynZbCBqHm9A,\"start\",\"end\"":{"s":{"x":"U35ZbzLo8UbynZbCBqHm9A","i":[{"t":"s"},{"t":"t","i":["XjXAKHOOdS7S",1],"o":"start","l":55,"c":"Myth 11: “Mass migration has produced mass segregation”","b":[{"t":"a","x":"U35ZbzLo8UbynZbCBqHm9A","l":"","i":["XjXAKHOOdS7S",56],"s":{"i":["XjXAKHOOdS7S",1],"a":"b"},"e":{"i":"end","a":"b"},"a":["b"]}]},{"t":"e","b":[]}],"l":""},"c":[]}}}},"crdt_format_version":1,"created_time":1758809362633,"last_edited_time":1758809362689,"parent_id":"277a8836-e820-80e3-88ef-cbe1c00c3dd0","parent_table":"block","alive":true,"created_by_table":"notion_user","created_by_id":"222d872b-594c-8128-886d-0002585be925","last_edited_by_table":"notion_user","last_edited_by_id":"222d872b-594c-8128-886d-0002585be925"},"role":"editor"}},"279a8836-e820-80b5-9ec7-d92501ad6d9a":{"spaceId":"8c4a8836-e820-8133-9c30-00030263b38c","value":{"value":{"id":"279a8836-e820-80b5-9ec7-d92501ad6d9a","space_id":"8c4a8836-e820-8133-9c30-00030263b38c","version":3,"type":"text","properties":{"title":[["Segregation is less the product of immigrants “clustering” voluntarily and more the outcome of socioeconomic inequality and discriminatory housing markets. Migrant communities often cluster for support, affordability, and safety, but residential segregation largely reflects broader class divisions. Over time, second and third generations tend to disperse geographically and socially. Thus, “mass segregation” is overstated and misused to stoke fears of cultural fragmentation."]]},"crdt_data":{"title":{"r":"7keLPzbhxDioUVFzwydkMw,\"start\",\"end\"","n":{"7keLPzbhxDioUVFzwydkMw,\"start\",\"end\"":{"s":{"x":"7keLPzbhxDioUVFzwydkMw","i":[{"t":"s"},{"t":"t","i":["_rMuMt-M_z-D",1],"o":"start","l":478,"c":"Segregation is less the product of immigrants “clustering” voluntarily and more the outcome of socioeconomic inequality and discriminatory housing markets. Migrant communities often cluster for support, affordability, and safety, but residential segregation largely reflects broader class divisions. Over time, second and third generations tend to disperse geographically and socially. Thus, “mass segregation” is overstated and misused to stoke fears of cultural fragmentation."},{"t":"e"}],"l":""},"c":[]}}}},"crdt_format_version":1,"created_time":1758809362635,"last_edited_time":1758809362689,"parent_id":"277a8836-e820-80e3-88ef-cbe1c00c3dd0","parent_table":"block","alive":true,"created_by_table":"notion_user","created_by_id":"222d872b-594c-8128-886d-0002585be925","last_edited_by_table":"notion_user","last_edited_by_id":"222d872b-594c-8128-886d-0002585be925"},"role":"editor"}},"279a8836-e820-807f-9000-eb2341a859a0":{"spaceId":"8c4a8836-e820-8133-9c30-00030263b38c","value":{"value":{"id":"279a8836-e820-807f-9000-eb2341a859a0","space_id":"8c4a8836-e820-8133-9c30-00030263b38c","version":4,"type":"sub_sub_header","properties":{"title":[["Myth 13: “Emigration leads to a brain drain”",[["b"]]]]},"crdt_data":{"title":{"r":"1TpB2b_g3XQgeooC8ww6Nw,\"start\",\"end\"","n":{"1TpB2b_g3XQgeooC8ww6Nw,\"start\",\"end\"":{"s":{"x":"1TpB2b_g3XQgeooC8ww6Nw","i":[{"t":"s"},{"t":"t","i":["GWwlB-hSaY5t",1],"o":"start","l":44,"c":"Myth 13: “Emigration leads to a brain drain”","b":[{"t":"a","x":"1TpB2b_g3XQgeooC8ww6Nw","l":"","i":["GWwlB-hSaY5t",45],"s":{"i":["GWwlB-hSaY5t",1],"a":"b"},"e":{"i":"end","a":"b"},"a":["b"]}]},{"t":"e","b":[]}],"l":""},"c":[]}}}},"crdt_format_version":1,"created_time":1758809362636,"last_edited_time":1758809362689,"parent_id":"277a8836-e820-80e3-88ef-cbe1c00c3dd0","parent_table":"block","alive":true,"created_by_table":"notion_user","created_by_id":"222d872b-594c-8128-886d-0002585be925","last_edited_by_table":"notion_user","last_edited_by_id":"222d872b-594c-8128-886d-0002585be925"},"role":"editor"}},"279a8836-e820-80d4-af82-c6b58b1b8962":{"spaceId":"8c4a8836-e820-8133-9c30-00030263b38c","value":{"value":{"id":"279a8836-e820-80d4-af82-c6b58b1b8962","space_id":"8c4a8836-e820-8133-9c30-00030263b38c","version":3,"type":"text","properties":{"title":[["De Haas critiques the simplistic notion of “brain drain.” While emigration of highly skilled workers can create short-term skill gaps in sending countries, it also brings benefits through remittances, skill circulation, and diaspora networks. Many emigrants return with new skills (“brain gain”), while others invest in their home countries from abroad. The impacts are mixed and context-dependent, not uniformly harmful. The brain-drain narrative often underestimates these positive feedback loops."]]},"crdt_data":{"title":{"r":"iHUWgK7mhl1ZWM8UXYygqQ,\"start\",\"end\"","n":{"iHUWgK7mhl1ZWM8UXYygqQ,\"start\",\"end\"":{"s":{"x":"iHUWgK7mhl1ZWM8UXYygqQ","i":[{"t":"s"},{"t":"t","i":["EWM8L6I0n4TU",1],"o":"start","l":499,"c":"De Haas critiques the simplistic notion of “brain drain.” While emigration of highly skilled workers can create short-term skill gaps in sending countries, it also brings benefits through remittances, skill circulation, and diaspora networks. Many emigrants return with new skills (“brain gain”), while others invest in their home countries from abroad. The impacts are mixed and context-dependent, not uniformly harmful. The brain-drain narrative often underestimates these positive feedback loops."},{"t":"e"}],"l":""},"c":[]}}}},"crdt_format_version":1,"created_time":1758809362638,"last_edited_time":1758809362689,"parent_id":"277a8836-e820-80e3-88ef-cbe1c00c3dd0","parent_table":"block","alive":true,"created_by_table":"notion_user","created_by_id":"222d872b-594c-8128-886d-0002585be925","last_edited_by_table":"notion_user","last_edited_by_id":"222d872b-594c-8128-886d-0002585be925"},"role":"editor"}},"279a8836-e820-8059-aa0f-fd064ee949c8":{"spaceId":"8c4a8836-e820-8133-9c30-00030263b38c","value":{"value":{"id":"279a8836-e820-8059-aa0f-fd064ee949c8","space_id":"8c4a8836-e820-8133-9c30-00030263b38c","version":4,"type":"sub_sub_header","properties":{"title":[["Myth 21: “Border restrictions reduce immigration”",[["b"]]]]},"crdt_data":{"title":{"r":"yA0ne-gWo6nNU8LqMNnjOw,\"start\",\"end\"","n":{"yA0ne-gWo6nNU8LqMNnjOw,\"start\",\"end\"":{"s":{"x":"yA0ne-gWo6nNU8LqMNnjOw","i":[{"t":"s"},{"t":"t","i":["cKSWGQ0RKfT0",1],"o":"start","l":49,"c":"Myth 21: “Border restrictions reduce immigration”","b":[{"t":"a","x":"yA0ne-gWo6nNU8LqMNnjOw","l":"","i":["cKSWGQ0RKfT0",50],"s":{"i":["cKSWGQ0RKfT0",1],"a":"b"},"e":{"i":"end","a":"b"},"a":["b"]}]},{"t":"e","b":[]}],"l":""},"c":[]}}}},"crdt_format_version":1,"created_time":1758809362638,"last_edited_time":1758809362689,"parent_id":"277a8836-e820-80e3-88ef-cbe1c00c3dd0","parent_table":"block","alive":true,"created_by_table":"notion_user","created_by_id":"222d872b-594c-8128-886d-0002585be925","last_edited_by_table":"notion_user","last_edited_by_id":"222d872b-594c-8128-886d-0002585be925"},"role":"editor"}},"279a8836-e820-8052-a537-f62e72dc3caf":{"spaceId":"8c4a8836-e820-8133-9c30-00030263b38c","value":{"value":{"id":"279a8836-e820-8052-a537-f62e72dc3caf","space_id":"8c4a8836-e820-8133-9c30-00030263b38c","version":3,"type":"text","properties":{"title":[["Counterintuitively, stricter borders often increase permanent immigration. When borders are open or flexible, migrants circulate more freely, returning home and moving back and forth. Restrictive policies trap migrants inside host countries because leaving risks not being able to return. This creates larger settled populations rather than reducing them. De Haas shows that policies often backfire, producing unintended consequences opposite to political intent."]]},"crdt_data":{"title":{"r":"4MYjQNFbDQ6qyXyEc5I7Cg,\"start\",\"end\"","n":{"4MYjQNFbDQ6qyXyEc5I7Cg,\"start\",\"end\"":{"s":{"x":"4MYjQNFbDQ6qyXyEc5I7Cg","i":[{"t":"s"},{"t":"t","i":["TZllxsAgZxiR",1],"o":"start","l":463,"c":"Counterintuitively, stricter borders often increase permanent immigration. When borders are open or flexible, migrants circulate more freely, returning home and moving back and forth. Restrictive policies trap migrants inside host countries because leaving risks not being able to return. This creates larger settled populations rather than reducing them. De Haas shows that policies often backfire, producing unintended consequences opposite to political intent."},{"t":"e"}],"l":""},"c":[]}}}},"crdt_format_version":1,"created_time":1758809362639,"last_edited_time":1758809362689,"parent_id":"277a8836-e820-80e3-88ef-cbe1c00c3dd0","parent_table":"block","alive":true,"created_by_table":"notion_user","created_by_id":"222d872b-594c-8128-886d-0002585be925","last_edited_by_table":"notion_user","last_edited_by_id":"222d872b-594c-8128-886d-0002585be925"},"role":"editor"}},"279a8836-e820-80c1-b610-ef5eabca4dfe":{"spaceId":"8c4a8836-e820-8133-9c30-00030263b38c","value":{"value":{"id":"279a8836-e820-80c1-b610-ef5eabca4dfe","space_id":"8c4a8836-e820-8133-9c30-00030263b38c","version":2,"type":"divider","crdt_data":{"title":{"r":"UWSQs6MLbvQ4KCy-cGnCIg,\"start\",\"end\"","n":{"UWSQs6MLbvQ4K